## Docker To Host Redirect/Routing Fix
1. Always use host.docker.internal to point to mention the URI of the Localhost or Host machine, inside the Docker containers

Ref: https://medium.com/@TimvanBaarsen/how-to-connect-to-the-docker-host-from-inside-a-docker-container-112b4c71bc66



# Build Issues:
1. Newtonsoft.Json reference: 'Newtonsoft.Json, Version=9.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=30ad4fe6b2a6aeed' or one of its dependencies. The system cannot find the file specified.
Fix: change the user folder name to current system user in docker-compose.yml file of each API folder